a critical patient.

433
00:27:12,370 --> 00:27:14,480
Play back all the previous clips.

434
00:27:14,480 --> 00:27:16,910
To see from where and
why he was running.

435
00:27:25,010 --> 00:27:27,920
Even if the patient
experiences an emergency,

436
00:27:27,920 --> 00:27:30,540
if you wish to deny...

437
00:27:30,540 --> 00:27:32,750
CPR and intubation...

438
00:27:33,770 --> 00:27:35,770
then you must sign the agreement.

439
00:27:37,010 --> 00:27:38,590
Please come with me.

440
00:27:42,700 --> 00:27:44,200
- Doctor.
