441
00:27:44,200 --> 00:27:46,000
Yu Ri Hye has an arrest.

442
00:27:46,000 --> 00:27:47,200
[ Cardiac arrest: Failure
of the heart to pump ]

443
00:27:52,500 --> 00:27:54,010
Doctor Kang.

444
00:27:54,010 --> 00:27:57,440
- My sister...
- I understand.

445
00:28:00,720 --> 00:28:03,140
Yu Ri Hye is in Code Blue.

446
00:28:13,650 --> 00:28:14,880
Her rate is dropping.

447
00:28:14,880 --> 00:28:16,370
So is her saturation.

448
00:28:27,310 --> 00:28:29,470
It's a DNR.

449
00:28:29,470 --> 00:28:31,390
[ DNR: Do Not Resuscitate ]

450
00:28:43,130 --> 00:28:44,400
Dr. Cha.

451
00:28:45,500 --> 00:28:46,630
Please stop.

452
00:28:47,660 --> 00:28:49,680
The patient composed
an advance directive,

453
00:28:49,680 --> 00:28:51,960
and the guardian consented.
You can't do this.

454
00:29:00,050 --> 00:29:02,820
[ I give my consent to
Yu Ri Hye's DNR order ]

455
00:29:12,560 --> 00:29:14,560
Can I see my sister...

