00:29:23,540 --> 00:29:24,660
[ Min Sung's Dad ]

459
00:29:25,900 --> 00:29:27,970
I'm sorry, please excuse me.

460
00:29:27,970 --> 00:29:29,840
Hello?

461
00:29:31,640 --> 00:29:33,990
What? Why would Min Sung...

462
00:29:36,290 --> 00:29:38,250
What are you talking about?

463
00:29:38,250 --> 00:29:40,610
Are you saying you lied?

464
00:29:42,160 --> 00:29:44,430
Min Sung is at the
hospital right now?

465
00:29:45,650 --> 00:29:47,700
Here's the emergency kit.
Please make way.

466
00:29:47,700 --> 00:29:48,960
Move aside!

467
00:29:48,960 --> 00:29:51,890
Dr. Cha, you can't be doing this.

468
00:29:51,890 --> 00:29:54,100
Everyone, get the intubation ready.

469
00:29:54,100 --> 00:29:56,250
Increase epinephrine
every three minutes.

470
00:30:02,320 --> 00:30:03,720
Ambu.

471
00:30:05,820 --> 00:30:07,380
Get the Ambu ready.

