00:30:28,290 --> 00:30:30,820
It's not that her son
didn't want to come.

476
00:30:30,820 --> 00:30:31,640
Then what was it?

477
00:30:31,640 --> 00:30:34,710
His dad didn't send him,
saying he'd fall into shock.

478
00:30:34,710 --> 00:30:38,500
After she fell from the rooftop,
