00:31:46,120 --> 00:31:47,530
Are you Min Sung?

496
00:31:47,530 --> 00:31:53,630
♫ For yesterday and feel the pain ♫

497
00:31:53,630 --> 00:31:55,100
Min Sung.

498
00:31:56,270 --> 00:31:57,990
Are you here for your mom?

